    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smooth, and has been well-loved over the years. This is the perfect find for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great in the driveway. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
