    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next big adventure! Everything runs smoothly and the interior is super clean. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road without that 'brand new' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
