      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Maintenance is up to date with a reinforced rear subframe and serviced VANOS system, addressing critical chassis and valvetrain longevity. The suspension geometry remains precise, offering communicative feedback through the apex. While it shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver's car, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression and a linear torque curve. This is a visceral, analog performance machine for the serious enthusiast.",
